example:
Input: root = [3,9,20,null,null,15,7]
Output: [[3],[9,20],[15,7]]
Input: root = [1]
Output: [[1]]
Input: root = []
Output: []
constraint: The number of nodes in the tree is in the range [0, 2000]. Node values are in the range [-1000, 1000].
title: Binary Tree Level Order Traversal
